
RandomizedTesting. Spikes and experiments.
https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-3492

Quickstart: 
 - open the projects in eclipse (m2e plugin or mvn eclipse:eclipse and import).
 
 - check out simple examples in randomizedtesting-examples.
 - run: mvn verify and see the test reports 
 
 - check out unit tests of randomizedtesting-runner, they provide coverage of all features.

